<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <title>Eats 메뉴뽑기</title>  
</head>

<body>
<header>
  <% include template/header %>
</header>

<!-- ======= Contact Section ======= -->
<section>
  <div class="container" data-aos="fade-up">

    <div class="section-title">
      <h2>1. 위치 찾기</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="row mt-1 mb-5">
      <div class="col-lg-12">
        <!-- 위치 찾기 -->
        <div class="row mb-2">
          <div class="col-md-12 text-center">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-12">
                <!-- <span id="postCodeData">현재 위치 정보</span> -->
                <span id="postCodeData"><span style="color: red;">위치 정보 없음</span></span>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-12">
                <button type="button" id="postCodeBtn" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">위치 찾기</button>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- 위치 찾기 종료 -->
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section-title">
      <h2>2. 검색어</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="row mt-1 mb-5">
      <div class="col-lg-12">
        <!-- 음식 종류 선택 -->
        <div class="row mb-2">
          <div class="col-sm-12">
            <div class="text-center">
              <p>검색어를 정확하게 입력하지 않을시 데이터가 정확하지 않을 수 있습니다!<br/>ex) 한식, 중식, 일식, 양식, 중식, 파스타, 맛집 등</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="col-md-12 text-center">
            <div class="col-md-12">
              <input type="text" id="keyword" placeholder="한식">
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-12">
              <span>위치 기준 거리 : </span>
              <input type="radio" name="radius" id="radius1" value="300" checked>
              <label for="radius1">300m</label>
              <input type="radio" name="radius" id="radius2" value="500">
              <label for="radius2">500m</label>
              <input type="radio" name="radius" id="radius3" value="1000">
              <label for="radius3">1km</label>
              <input type="radio" name="radius" id="radius4" value="1500">
              <label for="radius4">1.5Km</label>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-12">
              <span>오픈 여부 : </span>
              <input type="radio" name="opennow" id="opennow1" value="N" checked>
              <label for="opennow1">모두검색</label>
              <input type="radio" name="opennow" id="opennow2" value="Y">
              <label for="opennow2">오픈 가게만 검색</label>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-12">
              <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" id="foodSearchBtn">음식점 찾기</button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- 음식 종류 선택 종료 -->
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section-title">
      <h2>3. 결과</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="row mt-1 mb-5">
      <div class="col-lg-12">
        <!-- 결과 맵 -->
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-12 text-center">
            <p>결과 리스트</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-1"></div>
          <div class="col-10">
            <div id="map" style="width:100%;height:400px;"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
        <!-- 결과 맵 종료 -->
    </div>
  </div>
  <!-- Modal -->
  <div id="modal" class="modal fade" data-bs-backdrop="static" role="dialog">
    <div class="modal-dialog">
      <!-- Modal content-->
      <div class="modal-content">
        <div class="modal-header">
          <h4 class="modal-title">뽑기 중</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="modal-body">
          <p>검색 결과와 추천 음식점을 뽑는 중입니다. 잠시만 기다려주세요!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="modal-footer">
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
  <!-- Modal -->
</section>
<footer>
  <% include template/footer %>
</footer>
</body>
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/axios/dist/axios.min.js"></script>
<script src="//t1.daumcdn.net/mapjsapi/bundle/postcode/prod/postcode.v2.js"></script>
<!-- <script type="text/javascript" src="https://openapi.map.naver.com/openapi/v3/maps.js?ncpClientId=<%=process.env.NAVER_CLOUD_ID%>&callback=initNaverMap&submodules=geocoder"></script> -->
<script async defer src="https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/js?key=<%=process.env.GOOGLE_API_KEY%>" type="text/javascript"></script>
<script src="//dapi.kakao.com/v2/maps/sdk.js?appkey=<%=process.env.KAKAO_API_KEY%>&libraries=services"></script>
<script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.5.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
<script src="/js/eats.js"></script>
</html>